knowledge_panel.description: super mario 64 is a 1996 platform game for the nintendo 64 and the first super mario game to feature 3d gameplay. it was developed by nintendo ead and published by nintendo. super mario 64 features 3-dimensional freedom of movement within a large open world based on 3d polygons. wikipedia
